OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C'critical incident' amid New Year's
OL,5,CEve warning
OL,7,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service has
OL,8,Fdeclared a "critical incident" because
OL,9,Fof significantly increased demand
OL,10,Facross the 999 service and extensive
OL,11,Fhandover delays.
OL,13,FThe service says more than 340 calls
OL,14,Fwere waiting to be answered at the
OL,15,Ftime the critical incident was
OL,16,Fdeclared on the evening of Monday, 30
OL,17,FDecember, while more than half of the
OL,18,Ftrust's ambulances were waiting to
OL,19,Fhand over patients outside hospitals,
OL,20,Fleading to some people waiting "many
OL,21,Fhours" for an ambulance.
