OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C'critical incident' amid New Year's
OL,5,CEve warning
OL,7,FThe under-pressure service has now
OL,8,Furged New Year's Eve revellers to
OL,9,Fdrink in moderation to help reduce
OL,10,Fdemand on resources.
OL,12,FSpeaking on BBC Breakfast, chief
OL,13,Fexecutive Jason Killens said: "People
OL,14,Fout celebrating can help us tonight by
OL,15,Fof course, having a good time, but
OL,16,Fdrinking sensibly, eating before they
OL,17,Fgo out and looking after their
OL,18,Ffriends."
OL,20,FThe service has urged the public to
OL,21,Fcall 999 only for serious emergencies.
