OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C'critical incident' amid New Year's
OL,5,CEve warning
OL,7,F"I want to apologise to patients who
OL,8,Fwaited too long yesterday (Monday) and
OL,9,Fcontinue to wait this morning," Mr
OL,10,FKillens said.
OL,12,FAsked about the cause of the increased
OL,13,Fdemand, he said: "This pressure across
OL,14,Fthe health system is a result of flu
OL,15,Fand Covid and other respiratory
OL,16,Fviruses circulating through the winter.
OL,18,F"What we have seen in the last 24 to
OL,19,F48 hours is an acute accumulation of
OL,20,Fthose pressures."
