OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C'critical incident' amid New Year's
OL,5,CEve warning
OL,7,FSpeaking on Monday, head of service
OL,8,FStephen Sheldon said: "It is very rare
OL,9,Fthat we declare a critical incident,
OL,10,Fbut with significant demand on our
OL,11,Fservice and more than 90 ambulances
OL,12,Fwaiting to hand over patients outside
OL,13,Fof hospital, our ability to help
OL,14,Fpatients has been impacted.
OL,16,F"Regrettably, this means that some
OL,17,Fpatients will wait longer for an
OL,18,Fambulance to arrive and for their
OL,19,Fcalls to be answered. For that, we are
OL,20,Fvery sorry because this is not the
OL,21,Flevel of service we want to provide.
