OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C'critical incident' amid New Year's
OL,5,CEve warning
OL,7,F"We understand that this is
OL,8,Ffrustrating for patients, but can
OL,9,Fassure them that we are doing
OL,10,Feverything we can to relieve the
OL,11,Fpressure on our service.
OL,13,F"The public can help by only calling
OL,14,F999 in the event of a life-threatening
OL,15,Femergency - that's a cardiac arrest,
OL,16,Fchest pain or breathing difficulties,
OL,17,Floss of consciousness, choking or
OL,18,Fcatastrophic bleeding.
